1
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,920
Stay by my side…

2
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:12,439
and don't go anywhere.

3
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,800
Your mom said,

4
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:19,240
love isn't about doing
something for someone.

5
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:23,039
It's about putting your heart into it.

6
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:27,199
How are you involved with what happened
to Nut and his mother?

7
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:30,639
You're nosy because you're jealous
of Nut's mother, right?

8
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:33,319
Why would I be jealous?

9
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,680
Well, everybody loves her.

10
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,680
This includes Mr. Saen too.

11
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:41,719
Have you heard of the phrase

12
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:45,199
"Pity is the foundation of love"?

13
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:49,560
No. I've only heard of sympathy.

14
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,039
I'm off, Mom.

15
00:03:10,479 --> 00:03:11,439
Tofu.

16
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,680
Want to see the series you were in?

17
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:16,520
Juea just finished editing the teaser.

18
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:17,479
Do you?

19
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,479
I shouldn't.

20
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:24,719
I just went out yesterday.

21
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:27,919
I was going to help your mom
with the chores.

22
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:31,400
Don't worry about me.

23
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:34,280
I'm healthy now.
I can take care of myself.

24
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:37,159
You should do what you want,
so you don't get bored.

25
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:41,479
Maybe another time.

26
00:03:42,159 --> 00:03:44,360
I have a lot to do.

27
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:47,360
That's up to you. I'm off.

28
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,560
Bye.

29
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,479
Bye, Keunchai.

30
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,639
Song.

31
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,000
Oh, Tofu. What is it?

32
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:17,720
Song. Can you do me a favor?

33
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,079
Do you know

34
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:33,120
which close friend of Neung
has a name that begins with "T".

35
00:04:34,839 --> 00:04:35,959
Is it Thanayut,

36
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,480
Title,

37
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:40,639
or Tatarn?

38
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:44,839
Neung's close friend
with a name beginning with a "T"…

39
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,480
I think he's the only one.

40
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:49,959
Tatarn.

41
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:55,639
That one. They have a picture together.

42
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,160
This one?

43
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:01,360
That's right.

44
00:05:08,959 --> 00:05:12,199
Watch this. I just finished editing.

45
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,240
There.

46
