There's only one moon.

48
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,879
How about I draw another moon?

49
00:06:46,959 --> 00:06:48,480
If you draw another moon,

50
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:51,079
the first moon will lose its meaning.

51
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:00,720
Then one is enough.

